# Ignore everything in this folder
*

# Keep this .gitignore itself
!.gitignore

# Keep CustomPython and all files inside it
!CustomPython/
!CustomPython/**
# Drop Windows metadata that sneaks in there
CustomPython/**/[Dd]esktop.ini

# Keep DataLogs and all files inside it
!DataLogs/
!DataLogs/**
# Drop Windows metadata that sneaks in there
DataLogs/**/[Dd]esktop.ini

